xxl.core.indexStructures.builder.BPlusTree

Class BPlusTreeBuilder<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.indexStructures.builder.IndexBuilder<BPlusTreeBuilder,BPlusConfiguration.Creator>
      • xxl.core.indexStructures.builder.BPlusTree.BPlusTreeBuilder<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPropertyListSerializable<BPlusTreeBuilder,BPlusConfiguration.Creator>

    public class BPlusTreeBuilder<E>
extends IndexBuilder<BPlusTreeBuilder,BPlusConfiguration.Creator>
    A concrete implementation of IndexBuilder to easily create or restore an index with BPlusTree type. The construction especially the configuration like Containers, type management, storing in memory or persistent storage and so on depends on a given configuration set which is a BPlusConfiguration.Creator object.

    XXL provides a set of built-in builders, see sub classes of IndexBuilder.
    See Also:
    Setting up requirements for the BPlus tree, Base class for all index builders, The index structure itself
